    <briefdescription>
<para>Component debug drawing API. A condition based API which allows registering a condition per component type To conditionally run debug systems in the <ref refid="class_bvr_1_1_c_schedule" kindref="compound">Bvr::CSchedule</ref>. Registered conditions are visualised in the editor as a checkbox. Advised to use in conjunction with <ref refid="struct_bvr_1_1_gizmos" kindref="compound">Bvr::Gizmos</ref> to draw debug primitives. By default, engine provides draw systems for SMeshComponent, SPointLightComponent and SSpotLightComponent. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>embed:rst Usage:
*  =====
*  .. code-block:: c++
*      :emphasize-lines: 3, 5
* 
*      app
*          .AddSystem(SystemDesc(DrawSomeComp)
*          .WithCondition(Bvr::DebugDraw::CondFor&lt;T&gt;));
*           // Alternatively
*          .AddSystem(Bvr::DebugDraw::SystemDesc&lt;T&gt;(DrawSomeComp));
*  </verbatim> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
